import CategoricalScheme from '../../CategoricalScheme';

// TODO: add the colors to the theme while working on SIP https://github.com/apache/superset/issues/20159
const schemes = [
  {
    id: 'lyftColors',
    label: 'Lyft Colors',
    colors: [
      '#EA0B8C',
      '#6C838E',
      '#29ABE2',
      '#33D9C1',
      '#9DACB9',
      '#7560AA',
      '#2D5584',
      '#831C4A',
      '#333D47',
      '#AC2077',
    ],
  },
].map(s => new CategoricalScheme(s));

export default schemes;
